extends /includes/base
block content
    section#hero
        .hero-layer.paralax(style='background-image: url(/static/img/hero.team.jpg)' data-component='BgImage' data-props={field:'hero', defaultURL:'/static/img/hero.team.jpg'})
        .hero-layer.hero-layer-text.penguin-bg-image-sibling
            .hero-layer-text-v.active
                h1.bg-title.bgt-2.penguin-sp
                    span(data-component='Inplace' data-props={field: 'title'}) Our Team
        span#hero-arrow
    .wrapper3
        .text1
            p.big.text-center(data-component='Inplace' data-props={field: 'teaser'})
                | The success of our platform, a diversified ecosystem, is built upon global partnerships and collaboration across different sectors, including world-class universities and educational institutions, business and industry sectors, governments and third sector. Keeping standards high is important within the organisation, and “Only the Best” serves as a useful motto in this respect: we bring the world-best and make it available to all.
                
        .d-boss
            h3.text-center(data-component='Inplace' data-props={field: 'headline_director'}) DIRECTOR AND FOUNDER
            .team-member
                span.tm-img(style='background-image: url(/static/img/team1.jpg)' data-component='BgImage' data-props={field:'violet', defaultURL:'/static/img/team1.jpg'})
                strong(data-component='Inplace' data-props={field: 'violet-name'}) Dr. Violet Lo
                p(data-component='MediumEditor' data-props={field: 'violet-content'})
                  | After 13 years in investment banking, Violet decided to devote her time to Inclusive Business & Leadership, Social Investment & Innovation. She founded Inclusive Business Lab and Inclusive Business Foundation.
                    
        h3.text-center(style='padding-bottom: 50px;' data-component='Inplace' data-props={field: 'headline_nextgen'}) NEXT GEN LEADERS
        .text-center
          a.btn.btn-large(href='#' data-component="TeamAddButton" style='margin-bottom: 20px;') Add Leader
          
        ul.team-list(data-component="TeamList")
